{"tid":2096924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Whatsapp據報暫停處理香港當局取用戶數據要求","createTime":"2020-07-06T12:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T12:55:09.000Z","uid":205162,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf6af806f98d2cda4a5e1fe43c5614702150fd0","tid":2096924,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp據報暫停處理香港當局取用戶數據要求<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，因應香港實施國安法，即時通訊軟件Whatsapp已經暫停處理香港執法機構對用戶數據的要求。公司發言人回應《華爾街日報》查詢時說，正在暫停此類的審查要求，以便就《港版國安法》的影響進行評估，包括正式的人權盡職調查以及與人權專家磋商。報道說，長期以來，包括Facebook，WhatsApp、Instagram及Twitter和YouTube等一直在香港自由運營，不受中國互聯網「防火牆」限制。而香港的居民亦已經習慣透過社交平台發表政見和支持抗議。但是近日有使用者擔心國安法，紛紛刪除帳戶。而另一個社交平台telegram亦表示，從未與香港當局分享資料。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-06 20:30:08<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmAcVOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmAcVOX.png&h=3befa802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb36710e240598953cf8d658dba7edf6a2cbf55b","tid":2096924,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430a177e1bd6bc0dc790c2d2c632807c2f430522","tid":2096924,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e508bcdfc37b243fd8a8d6c6cfda2943f8956c15","tid":2096924,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" clas